About Us
House Blend Mission
Giving Back
Volunteer
Merch
House Blend Cafe is more than just a place to grab a bite—it’s a space where community and purpose come together. Since opening our doors in 2006, our mission has been simple: to serve great food and make a meaningful impact on the lives of others. We believe in the power of connection, whether through a shared meal, a cup of locally roasted coffee, or joining together to support important causes.
At House Blend Cafe, we offer a warm, welcoming atmosphere where you can enjoy freshly made breakfast, lunch, and dinner options that bring people together. But our commitment doesn’t end with food. We donate 100% of our net profits to local and global projects that focus on ending hunger, combating human trafficking, and supporting foster care and adoption services. Every meal served helps support the greater good.
Come for the food, stay for the mission. We invite you to be part of the House Blend Cafe family, where community, compassion, and great coffee are always on the menu.
